description: Chicken Nuggetry is the must have skill for all chicken nugget lovers.  With tons of sweet and sour chicken nugget haikus for your pleasure. Once you have enabled the skill, just say "Alexa, open nugget haikus" and enjoy!
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask nugget haikus for a haiku
Alexa, ask nugget haikus to tell me a haiku
name: Chicken Nuggetry
shortDescription: Love chicken nuggets? Listen to all the chicken nugget haikus your heart can handle.
